  "commit_message": "fix(module-source): ship src-xs/ so the xs export condition resolves\n\n`exports['.'].xs` points at `./src-xs/index.js`, but `src-xs` was not\nlisted in `files`, so neither the staged tarball nor the npm-published\n4.3.0 release contains it. XS-engine consumers resolving the `xs`\ncondition would hit ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND — silently broken for as long\nas the conditional export has existed.\n\nSurfaced by ts-node-pack's validator, which (unlike `npm pack`) checks\nthat every `exports` leaf resolves to a r",
